## **🚀 Quick Start (Phase 1 Preview)**

### **Build Instructions** (Coming in Phase 1)

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://gogs.dclub.kr/kim/mlir-formal-semantics.git
cd mlir-formal-semantics

# Install dependencies
./scripts/install-deps.sh

# Build MLIR with verification passes
mkdir build && cd build
cmake -DMLIR_DIR=/path/to/mlir/build ..
make -j$(nproc)

# Run tests
ctest
```

### **Usage Example** (Coming in Phase 1)

```bash
# Verify a transformation
mlir-opt input.mlir \
  -formal-semantic-verification \
  -verify-report output.json

# Output: JSON with PASS/FAIL and counterexamples (if any)
```

